{"slug": "potion", "root": "potion", "category": "alchemy", "gloss": "a prepared magical draught", "is_keyword": false, "etymology": {"lang": "Latin", "origin": "Latin potio 'a drink' (potare 'to drink')", "first": "c. 1300", "note": "'Poison' is the very same Latin word arriving by a different French road — a potion and a poison are perfect etymological twins.", "hook": "Potion and poison: one Latin word, two fates."}, "essay": null, "sources": ["Etymonline (Douglas Harper)", "Wiktionary", "classical lexica (Lewis & Short, LSJ, Bosworth–Toller)", "Ted's historical-magic DBs (WitchcraftStudiesDB, AgrippaDOP, MedievalMagicDB)"], "stats": {"flavor_total": 17, "oracle_total": 0, "in_flavor_cards": 13, "in_oracle_cards": 0, "name_match_count": 3, "by_variant": {"potions": 11, "potion": 6}, "first_year": 1995, "colors": {"R": 3, "W": 5, "G": 4, "B": 4, "U": 1}, "by_year": {"1995": 1, "2001": 2, "2009": 1, "2010": 1, "2011": 1, "2018": 1, "2021": 2, "2024": 2, "2025": 3, "2026": 2}}, "cards": [{"id": "2fcca686-03c8-4407-9f9f-2b7462470044", "name": "Alabaster Potion", "set": "ME3", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "uncommon", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/c/8ce1f383-258d-4fa1-a3c7-3424bb2e568c.jpg?1782753389", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/c/8ce1f383-258d-4fa1-a3c7-3424bb2e568c.jpg?1782753389", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/me3/2/alabaster-potion?utm_source=api", "local": "img/potion/2fcca686-03c8-4407-9f9f-2b7462470044.jpg"}, {"id": "11fb3fee-ae84-4bf3-b834-63d3b8987df3", "name": "Potion of Healing", "set": "AFR", "type_line": "Artifact", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/d/5/d5edb608-c7d7-4fa9-b969-262c9789fc17.jpg?1782704422", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/d/5/d5edb608-c7d7-4fa9-b969-262c9789fc17.jpg?1782704422", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/afr/34/potion-of-healing?utm_source=api", "local": "img/potion/11fb3fee-ae84-4bf3-b834-63d3b8987df3.jpg"}, {"id": "c8fbcef0-2cbf-4a59-8322-374dd9153ebf", "name": "Sleeping Potion", "set": "PLS", "type_line": "Enchantment — Aura", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/6/f/6f79f4b2-71cd-4f78-a161-d75b162c745e.jpg?1782719929", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/6/f/6f79f4b2-71cd-4f78-a161-d75b162c745e.jpg?1782719929", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/pls/34/sleeping-potion?utm_source=api", "local": "img/potion/c8fbcef0-2cbf-4a59-8322-374dd9153ebf.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Elder Auntie", "set": "ECL", "html": "&quot;Did nephew spit up again? Oh, good! Auntie needed to make a new batch of <mark>potions</mark> for the merrow market.&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/4/84678e98-2258-4ea1-aaf0-8ac4cc2ecf8d.jpg?1782684027"}, {"card": "Leeches", "set": "ME4", "html": "&quot;Where our <mark>potions</mark> and powders fail, perhaps nature will succeed.&quot;\n—Reyhan, Samite Alchemist", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/6/a6028e2c-486b-40f8-8b74-7150eb72b9f1.jpg?1782752768"}, {"card": "Samite Alchemist", "set": "HML", "html": "&quot;Powders and <mark>potions</mark> are nothing compared to faith.&quot;\n—Baris, Serra Inquisitor", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/8/68224871-d4c2-4b43-9ab8-c0685588b035.jpg?1782721599"}, {"card": "Preposterous Proportions", "set": "FDN", "html": "Their acorn hunt was unsuccessful, but they did find the wizard&#x27;s experimental <mark>potion</mark> cache.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/c/acb65189-60e4-42e0-9fb1-da6b716b91d7.jpg?1782689171"}, {"card": "Bazaar Trader", "set": "WWK", "html": "&quot;No need for a hurda? How about these maps to recently discovered tombs? Or these vials of invisible <mark>potion</mark>? Very fancy . . .&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/2/9235ef13-a363-4cab-b69d-39093a621a5c.jpg?1782715556"}, {"card": "Grow Extra Arms", "set": "SPM", "html": "&quot;I created that <mark>potion</mark> to rob me of my spider-powers. I wanted it to change me forever. But not like this! NOT LIKE THIS!&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/3/63fab399-00db-4398-922e-c3ca3356731a.jpg?1782684838"}, {"card": "Bile-Vial Boggart", "set": "ECL", "html": "It took years to finesse his <mark>potion</mark> of necroskitter slime and bogslither teeth. Finally, *he* would prank the fae.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/c/2c0fcf98-1f3c-4cff-9234-7f3d0c8b22e9.jpg?1782684074"}, {"card": "Eyetwitch", "set": "STX", "html": "Oculomancers see the ideal <mark>potion</mark> ingredient. The bats don&#x27;t see it that way.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/f/1f4d1bb6-cb8f-4d01-9879-0b3a0585cbf4.jpg?1782704970"}, {"card": "Stadium Vendors", "set": "BBD", "html": "&quot;<mark>Potions</mark>! Mana <mark>potions</mark>, health <mark>potions</mark>, energy <mark>potions</mark>—get your <mark>potions</mark> here!&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/d/2d25baa1-4794-4bed-bf0c-7d99f39f9656.jpg?1782709995"}, {"card": "Revitalizing Repast // Old-Growth Grove", "set": "MH3", "html": "&quot;Today, we feast! Tomorrow, we fight! Then, we feast again!&quot;\n—Harald, king of Skemfar\nThe most potent elvish tonics and <mark>potions</mark> are brewed from the trees containing their imprisoned gods, the Einir.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/3/03522b6b-31ec-4126-8885-5dbb2248688b.jpg?1782691146"}, {"card": "Stiltzkin, Moogle Merchant", "set": "FIN", "html": "&quot;How about a three-piece combo of Hi-<mark>Potion</mark>, Ether, and Phoenix Pinion for 444 Gil?&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/6/06a972a4-0c1b-4f12-a5a5-fdea47c4cd35.jpg?1782686573"}, {"card": "Goobbue Gardener", "set": "FIN", "html": "The parasitic moss that grows in the folds of the goobbue&#x27;s back is highly valued as an ingredient in various <mark>potions</mark> and medicines.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/7/b7c3544a-5dd5-423e-8a40-ac4803db8adc.jpg?1782686457"}, {"card": "Mournful Zombie", "set": "APC", "html": "Treated with a powerful mix of herbs and <mark>potions</mark>, its wrappings have a remarkable preservative effect, even for the living.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/b/9ba12fb1-de8c-46c6-b33f-e0580ed2a3ee.jpg?1782719501"}], "mechanics_snippets": [], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/4/84678e98-2258-4ea1-aaf0-8ac4cc2ecf8d.jpg?1782684027", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/4/84678e98-2258-4ea1-aaf0-8ac4cc2ecf8d.jpg?1782684027", "card": "Elder Auntie"}}